#Author: persist
#Abstract: install Chinese input method in English Ubuntu14.04

1. install fcitx language support framework. you can search 'fcitx' in Ubuntu Software Center to install 'Flexible Input Method Framework'
2. switch keyboard input method system to 'fcitx' in System Settings -> Language Support, don't forget to drag '汉语(中国)' to the first item in 'Language for menus and windows'
3. restart ubuntu system
4. add Chinese(Pinyin) in Text Entry

5. ???
